last_episode_to_air.overview: As Duane and crew explore the cavern they find themselves overcome by a deadly and invisible gas cloud. Complications with their rescue leaves them wondering if they will make it out alive.

name: Mystery at Blind Frog Ranch
overview: There are some places on earth where the land just seems different, and Blind Frog Ranch in eastern Utah is one of those places. Locals say the land is cursed. That it's trying to hold on to something.

episodes.name: What Lies Beneath
episodes.overview: Duane Ollinger sinks everything he has into hunting for what he believes is a vast fortune of gold on his property; with each step he takes closer to finding the treasure, the land appears to hold on tighter and stop him in his tracks.

episodes.name: No Dyin' Tryin' Today
episodes.overview: After a long winter, the crew returns to Blind Frog Ranch to strategize a new plan to get the box out of the underwater cave. And Charlie asks for help to investigate a mysterious death on the ranch.

episodes.name: Aztec or Not?
episodes.overview: The results from radiocarbon testing are in, which will tell Duane if the box is Aztec or not. Then, the men discover they are being surveilled by a high-tech camera mounted just above the cave entrance.

episodes.name: Diving Blind
episodes.overview: When a windstorm ruins visibility in the water, Chad considers a risky blind dive to extract the box. But when intruders are discovered, Duane and his crew realize that time is running out.

episodes.name: What's Inside the Box?
episodes.overview: Chad makes a huge mistake, derailing the operation to drag the box out of the cavern. But when they pull out some of the box's contents, they are shocked by what they discover.

episodes.name: Radioactive Rocks
episodes.overview: Determined to get into the cavern, Duane and his team explore new methods to find a dry entrance; while Chad takes to the skies in search of a natural opening, Eric thinks the radioactive rocks found in the box might show them where to dig.

episodes.name: The Void
episodes.overview: After Duane makes a costly mistake, Eric and Chad finally discover what they've been looking for. However, the crew gets caught in the cross hairs of mysterious intruders.

episodes.name: Down to the Center of the Earth
episodes.overview: After the crew drills into a dry cavern, they must devise a plan to protect themselves from radioactivity and poisonous gasses; but as they get close to finally entering the cave, trespassers descend upon the ranch.

episodes.name: Darkness, Danger and Death
episodes.overview: As Duane and crew explore the cavern they find themselves overcome by a deadly and invisible gas cloud. Complications with their rescue leaves them wondering if they will make it out alive.
